== 製作 ==
儘管《[[神隱任務|神隱任務]]》原本認為將會發展成一個{{link-en|強檔|Tent-pole (entertainment)}}電影系列，但在最初報導說，續集因在北美的口碑不佳而取消<ref>{{cite web|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|title=Tom Cruise's 'Jack Reacher' Unlikely to Get Sequel|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tom-cruises-jack-reacher-sequel-412465|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=2015-05-24|date=2013-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150426094114/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/tom-cruises-jack-reacher-sequel-412465|archive-date=2015-04-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年2月，電影在全球票房總計2億美元以上使得續集有望推出<ref>{{cite web|last=Trumbore|first=Dave|title=JACK REACHER Sequel Possibly in the Works at Paramount and Skydance|url=http://collider.com/jack-reacher-sequel/|work=Collider.com|accessdate=2015-05-24|date=2013-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724130351/http://collider.com/jack-reacher-sequel/|archive-date=2015-07-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年12月9日，宣布，[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]和{{link-en|天空之舞製片公司|Skydance Productions}}將負責製作，並會根據2013年的小說《{{link-en|永不回頭 (小說)|Never Go Back|永不-{}-回頭}}》作改編<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|title=Jack Reacher’s Back; Tom Cruise Developing New Bestseller ‘Never Go Back’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/jack-reachers-back-tom-cruise-developing-new-bestseller-never-go-back/|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2015-05-24|date=2013-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611094517/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/jack-reachers-back-tom-cruise-developing-new-bestseller-never-go-back/|archive-date=2014-06-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年5月14日，據報導，[[湯姆·克魯斯|湯姆·克魯斯]]將繼續出演[[傑克·李奇|傑克·李奇]]一角<ref>{{cite web|last=|first=|title=Jack Reacher 2 Movie To Bring Back ‘Top Gun’ Star Tom Cruise With A ‘Teenage Female Sidekick’ Based On Lee Child’s Novel ‘Never Go Back’|url=http://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/91535/20140514/jack-reacher-2-movie.htm|work=kpopstarz.com|publisher=|accessdate=2015-05-24|date=2014-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326032518/http://www.kpopstarz.com/articles/91535/20140514/jack-reacher-2-movie.htm|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月19日，據《Deadline》報導，[[愛德華·茲維克|愛德華·茲維克]]將執導電影，而劇本則由茲維克、李察·溫克和{{link-en|馬歇爾·赫斯高維基|Marshall Herskovitz}}重寫。在此之前，茲維克和赫斯高維基曾在《[[末代武士|末代武士]]》中一起與克魯斯合作<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fleming Jr|first1=Mike|title=Ed Zwick In Talks To Direct ‘Jack Reacher’ Sequel|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/jack-reacher-sequel-ed-zwick-director-paramount-1201429671/|accessdate=2015-05-24|work=deadline.com|date=2015-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521182451/http://deadline.com/2015/05/jack-reacher-sequel-ed-zwick-director-paramount-1201429671/|archive-date=2015-05-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年8月14日，[[蔻碧·史莫德|蔻碧·史莫德]]加入劇組飾演女主角<ref name=SmuldersCast>{{cite news|last1=Sneider|first1=Jeff|last2=Verhoeven|first2=Beatrice|title=‘Avengers’ Star Cobie Smulders Poised to Join Tom Cruise in ‘Jack Reacher 2’ (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/avengers-star-cobie-smulders-poised-to-join-tom-cruise-in-jack-reacher-2-exclusive/|accessdate=2015-08-16|work=thewrap.com|date=2015-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150816173641/http://www.thewrap.com/avengers-star-cobie-smulders-poised-to-join-tom-cruise-in-jack-reacher-2-exclusive/|archive-date=2015-08-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月15日，[[達妮卡·亞羅許|達妮卡·亞羅許]]簽約出演本片<ref name=YaroshCast>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=‘Jack Reacher’: ‘Heroes Reborn’ Actress Eyed to Join Tom Cruise (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jack-reacher-tom-cruise-danika-yarosh-1201594525/|accessdate=2