=== 拍攝 ===
正式攝製開始於2015年10月20日在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的[[紐奧良|紐奧良]]進行<ref name=Oct2015CS>{{cite news|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=Jack Reacher: Never Go Back Begins Filming with Tom Cruise|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/624203-jack-reacher-never-go-back-begins-filming-with-tom-cruise#/slide/1|accessdate=2015-10-21|work=comingsoon.net|date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021131508/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/624203-jack-reacher-never-go-back-begins-filming-with-tom-cruise#/slide/1|archive-date=2015-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年11月23日，劇組在[[巴頓魯治_(路易西安納州)|巴頓魯治]]取景<ref>{{cite news|title=‘Jack Reacher 2: Never Go Back’ Casting Call for Military in Baton Rouge|url=http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-acting-auditions/jack-reacher-2-never-go-back-casting-call-for-military-in-baton-rouge/|accessdate=2015-11-12|work=projectcasting.com|date=2015-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328234733/http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-acting-auditions/jack-reacher-2-never-go-back-casting-call-for-military-in-baton-rouge|archive-date=2016-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年1月，又移至[[聖弗瑞安斯維爾_(路易斯安那州)|聖弗瑞安斯維爾]]拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Erica|first1=Ells|title=Extras Casting Information for "Jack Reacher 2: Never Go Back" in NOLA - Auditions Free|url=http://www.auditionsfree.com/2016/extras-casting-information-jack-reacher-2-never-go-back-nola/|accessdate=2016-01-11|work=Auditions Free|date=2016-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160110062543/http://www.auditionsfree.com/2016/extras-casting-information-jack-reacher-2-never-go-back-nola/|archive-date=2016-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
2015年9月，派拉蒙排定電影2016年10月21日美國上映<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Tom Cruise’s ‘Jack Reacher 2’ Set for October 2016 Release|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jack-reacher-2-release-date-october-2016-1201583927/|accessdate=2015-09-06|work=variety.com|date=2015-09-02|archive-url=https://archive.li/20151022060104/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jack-reacher-2-release-date-october-2016-1201583927/|archive-date=2015-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，還釋出了官方網頁遊戲《''Jack Reacher: Never Stop Punching''》來宣傳電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/jack-reacher-video-game-has-a-great-name/1100-6443772/?ftag=GSS-05-10aaa0b|title=Jack Reacher Video Game Has a Great Name|first=Mat|last=Paget|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2016-09-21|accessdate=2016-09-21|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010192704/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/jack-reacher-video-game-has-a-great-name/1100-6443772/?ftag=GSS-05-10aaa0b|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年1月17日，影片[[数字发行|数字发行]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/7423/jack-reacher-2-never-go-back|website=DVDs Release Dates|title=Jack Reacher: Never Go Back|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118225636/http://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/7423/jack-reacher-2-never-go-back|archive-date=2016-11-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1月31日以[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]、4K Ultra HD和[[DVD|DVD]]格式发行<ref>{{cite web|title=Jack Reacher: Never Go Back Blu-ray and Digital HD Announcement|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/dvd/trailers/796795-jack-reacher-never-go-back-blu-ray#/slide/1|website=ComingSoon.net|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222174010/http://www.comingsoon.net/dvd/trailers/796795-jack-reacher-never-go-back-blu-ray#/slide/1|archive-date=2016-12-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Pacis|first1=Mark|title=Blu-ray details released for ‘Jack Reacher: Never Go Back'|url=http://nerdreactor.com/2016/12/20/jack-reacher-2-blu-ray-details/|website=Nerd Reactor|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223171703/http://nerdreactor.com/2016/12/20/jack-reacher-2-blu-ray-details/|archive-date=2016-12-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價===
《神隱任務：永不回頭》獲得的評價褒貶不一，但負評多過於好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度38%，基於176條評論，平均分為5.1/10<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jack_reacher_never_go_back |title= Jack Reacher: Never Go Back (2016) |publisher= Flixster |work= [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate= 2016-10-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161020162147/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jack_reacher_never_go_back |archive-date= 2016-10-20 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到47分，評價好壞各半參雜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/jack-reacher-never-go-back|title=Jack Reacher: Never Go Back|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027004058/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/jack-reacher-never-go-back|archive-date=2016-10-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的反應於A+至F間落在「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |access-date=2019-10-15 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20170916153548/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |archive-date=2017-09-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

