在美國，該片估計於首映週末能從三千五百間戲院中獲得2000萬美元的票房，儘管片商保守估計為1700萬美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/the-accountant-ben-affleck-kevin-hart-fall-box-office-ticket-sales-1201835284/ |title=Can Ben Affleck’s ‘The Accountant’ Be An Asset For Weak Fall Box Office? – Preview |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |access-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017193510/http://deadline.com/2016/10/the-accountant-ben-affleck-kevin-hart-fall-box-office-ticket-sales-1201835284/ |archive-date=2016-10-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=budget/>。美國首映週末票房僅2300萬美元，位居當週票房排名亞軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/weekend-box-office-boo-madea-940721|title=Box Office: 'Boo! A Madea Halloween' Scares Off Tom Cruise's 'Jack Reacher' With $27.6M|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-10-23|accessdate=2016-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024094313/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/weekend-box-office-boo-madea-940721|archive-date=2016-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/10/23/box-office-tom-cruises-jack-reacher-nabs-23m-weekend-ouija-gets-tomb-raider-trapped/#7f9cb2967162|title=Box Office: Tom Cruise's 'Jack Reacher' Nabs $23M Weekend, 'Ouija' Gets 'Tomb Raider' Trapped|author=Scott Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2016-10-23|accessdate=2016-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024090916/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/10/23/box-office-tom-cruises-jack-reacher-nabs-23m-weekend-ouija-gets-tomb-raider-trapped/#7f9cb2967162|archive-date=2016-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。台灣方面，最終全台票房為新台幣1.15億元<ref>{{cite book |author1=陳斌全總編輯 |title=台灣電影年鑑.2018 |date=2019-01 |publisher=國家電影中心 |location=臺北市 |isbn=978-986-96024-0-2 |pages=p.72-p.161 |edition=初版 |url=https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/中華民國電影年鑑民國107年.pdf |accessdate=2019-04-18 |archive-date=2019-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514200521/https://www.tfi.org.tw/Content/TFI/PublicInfo/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%B9%B4%E9%91%91%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B107%E5%B9%B4.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。中國大陸方面，最終票房為6100万人民币<ref>{{cite web |title=《侠探杰克：永不回头》電影介紹 |url=http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/249003 |website=貓眼票房 |accessdate=2020-10-09 |archive-date=2016-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161024170918/http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/249003 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

